{"tid":2178423,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]屯門區議員支持全民檢測","createTime":"2020-08-28T11:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T08:56:13.000Z","uid":64787,"like":3,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"aac21b6eb2e0fe27a0902a6e85e9d81fd5a17af8","tid":2178423,"uid":64787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzLLURJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzLLURJ.png&h=a11dc3a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/111709813684840/posts/189490585906762/?extid=kbnYZUrANNTWo1Y9&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F111709813684840%2Fposts%2F189490585906762%2F%3Fextid%3DkbnYZUrANNTWo1Y9%26d%3Dn&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=bd7c81dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/111709813684840/posts/189490585906762/?extid=kbnYZUrANNTWo1Y9&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"933d220ad625f54530212c3983102ff4d29ba46c","tid":2178423,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:11:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0128337abe59c2dbad5dc58c68349a22439a408d","tid":2178423,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"933d220ad625f54530212c3983102ff4d29ba46c","tid":2178423,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:11:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"前民主黨"},{"pid":"0493df215758f9de7cf33b8531d2e39606d0e500","tid":2178423,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:15:00.000Z","msg":"2019年區議會選舉\t編輯<br />\n主條目：2019年香港區議會選舉<br />\n2019年10月4日，林頌鎧向選舉事務處遞交提名參選2019年香港區議會選舉，同區還有報稱五金店東主，參選多屆的王加良競逐兆置選區議席。[18][19] 10月31日獲屯門民政專員、選舉主任馮雅慧確認提名有效。[20] 結果林頌鎧擊敗王加良成功連任，更取得5,798票，成為當屆屯門區議會的「票王」。[21]<br />\n<br />\n退出民主黨\t編輯<br />\n2020年1月2日，　 民主黨的屯門區議會[恆福]]選區議員朱順雅宣布退出　 民主黨，而根據香港01、蘋果日報及東方日報的報導，同屬　 民主黨的屯門區議會兆置選區議員林頌鎧亦已退黨。[22][23][24] 其後林表示已經退黨，以獨立身份繼續地區工作，暫時沒有打算加入其他政黨。[25]"},{"pid":"1de48354eebbc0ab3afd88201b71cfd9af77801a","tid":2178423,"uid":2110,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"0128337abe59c2dbad5dc58c68349a22439a408d","tid":2178423,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"933d220ad625f54530212c3983102ff4d29ba46c","tid":2178423,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:11:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"前民主黨"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"2020年1月2日，  民主黨的屯門區議會[恆福]]選區議員朱順雅宣布退出  民主黨，而根據香港01、蘋果日報及東方日報的報導，同屬  民主黨的屯門區議會兆置選區議員林頌鎧亦已退黨。[22][23][24] 其後林表示已經退黨，以獨立身份繼續地區工作，暫時沒有打算加入其他政黨。[25]<br />\n<br />\n條友一上任第2日就退黨<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9E%97%E9%A0%8C%E9%8E%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%25A0%258C%25E9%258E%25A7&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=ccc2fd67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9E%97%E9%A0%8C%E9%8E%A7</a>"},{"pid":"9c5c58f444a10c938dd302b0a4a89978219e0a23","tid":2178423,"uid":70786,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/mPJAQoY.jpg&amp;h=35e4ae8b&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"e691e18456f96ea8f647fe5b452671b7fd275fc5","tid":2178423,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1de48354eebbc0ab3afd88201b71cfd9af77801a","tid":2178423,"uid":2110,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"0128337abe59c2dbad5dc58c68349a22439a408d","tid":2178423,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"933d220ad625f54530212c3983102ff4d29ba46c","tid":2178423,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:11:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:12:34.000